# Windows supported file extensions

Here's a list of file extensions you can print from this module.

**N.B.**: not all extensions have been tested, so if you find some bug, please report me opening an issue

* .bmp
* .c
* .c++
* .cc
* .com
* .conf
* .css
* .gif
* .h
* .hh
* .htm
* .html
* .java
* .jpe
* .jpeg
* .jpg
* .js
* .log
* .pdf
* .png
* .tif
* .tiff
* .txt
